snippet.title: Beyond The Ice Palace 2 - Announcement Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Arise From The Dead & Claim Back Your Throne In 'Beyond The Ice Palace 2'!

Embark on a journey of vengeance and redemption as the 'Cursed King,' reclaiming your rightful throne in this action platformer.
